      "range": "0-45",
      "markText": "老君曰：大道無形，生育天地；大道無情，運行日月；大道無名，長養萬物。吾不知其名，強名曰道。",
      "totalCount": 976,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "793635_1_636-685",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "636-685",
      "markText": "夫人神好清而心擾之，人心好靜而慾牽之。常能遣其欲而心自靜，澄其心而神自清，自然六慾不生，三毒消滅。",
      "totalCount": 855,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=793635&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=636&rangeEnd=685",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc1325b05c1c23fc15e674e?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=636&rangeEnd=685"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "793635_1_1196-1267",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1196-1267",
      "markText": "觀空亦空，空無所空。所空既無，無無亦無。無無既無，湛然常寂。寂無所寂，欲豈能生？欲既不生，即是真靜。真常應物1，真常得性。常應常靜，常清靜矣。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=793635&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1196&rangeEnd=1267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc1325b05c1c23fc15e674e?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1196&rangeEnd=1267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "793635_1_1858-1943",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1858-1943",
      "markText": "眾生所以不得真道者，為有妄心。既有妄心，即驚其神。既驚其神，即著萬物。既著萬物，即生貪求。既生貪求，即是煩惱。煩惱妄想，憂苦身心，便遭濁辱，流浪生死，常沉苦海，永失真道。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=793635&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1858&rangeEnd=1943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc1325b05c1c23fc15e674e?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1858&rangeEnd=1943"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "793635_1_908-953",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "908-953",
      "markText": "能遣之者，內觀其心，心無其心；外觀其形，形無其形；遠觀其物，物無其物。三者既悟，惟見於空。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=793635&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=908&rangeEnd=953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc1325b05c1c23fc15e674e?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=908&rangeEnd=953"
    },
    {
